8"> </span><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="//www.jstor.org/stable/30233666" id="mwA6A">30233666</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Japanese+Journal+of+Religious+Studies&amp;rft.atitle=Shinto+Funerals+in+the+Edo+Period&amp;rft.volume=27&amp;rft.issue=3%2F4&amp;rft.pages=239-271&amp;rft.date=2000&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F30233666&amp;rft.aulast=Kenney&amp;rft.aufirst=Elizabeth&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AShinto" class="Z3988" about="#mwt186" id="mwA6E"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt186" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwA6I"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-34" id="cite_note-34"><a href="./Shinto#cite_ref-34" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-34" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt187" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite web","href":"./Template:Cite_web"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"http://classroom.synonym.com/shinto-funeral-beliefs-rituals-5894.html"},"title":{"wt":"Shinto Funeral Beliefs and Rituals"},"last":{"wt":""},"first":{"wt":""},"date":{"wt":""},"website":{"wt":""},"publisher":{"wt":""},"access-date":{"wt":""}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwA6M"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://classroom.synonym.com/shinto-funeral-beliefs-rituals-5894.html" id="mwA6Q">"Shinto Funeral Beliefs and Rituals"</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Shinto+Funeral+Beliefs+and+Rituals&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fclassroom.synonym.com%2Fshinto-funeral-beliefs-rituals-5894.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AShi