<li id="mwA_U"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://eos.kokugakuin.ac.jp/modules/xwords/" id="mwA_Y">Kokugakuin University Encyclopedia of Shinto</a> and its Japanese <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://21coe.kokugakuin.ac.jp/db/jinja/" id="mwA_c">Shinto Jinja Database</a></li>
